; Coverage for amount.cc lines 204, 206-207, 220:
; Negative amounts with standard comma thousands separator and period decimal.
; The negative sign goes through line 206-207 (out << *p for '-').
; The thousands separator goes through line 220 (out << ',').
; The decimal point goes through line 204 (out << *p for '.').

commodity $
    format $1,000.00

2024/01/01 Large Payment
    Expenses:Rent          $12,345.67
    Assets:Bank

test reg Assets
24-Jan-01 Large Payment         Assets:Bank             $-12,345.67  $-12,345.67
end test
